latestPosts.caption:
Pantheon Paris. 

"Standing before the Panthéon, where the echoes of greatness resonate through time. This iconic monument honors some of history’s most brilliant minds, including Marie Curie—the first woman laid to rest here for her own achievements. A place where science, literature, and philosophy converge, reminding us that legacies are built through passion and perseverance. ✨🇫🇷 #PantheonParis #MarieCurie #LegendsLiveOn"

latestPosts.caption:
"Upon this rock, I will build my Church." (Matthew 16:18)

Standing in the heart of Christendom, where faith transcends time and history echoes with the voices of saints. St. Peter’s Basilica—built upon the faith of the first Apostle, a symbol of God’s eternal promise. Here, in this sacred place, I am reminded that His Church stands strong, and so does my faith.
